E-Commerce Website
Features:
User Roles:

Admin: Manage products, orders, and users.
Customer: Browse products, add to cart, and place orders.
Product Management:

CRUD operations for products (Admin only).
Search and filter (by category, price, etc.).
Shopping Cart:

Add/remove items in the cart.
Update quantities and calculate totals.
Order Management:

Place orders, track status (pending, shipped, delivered).
View past orders.
Payment Integration:

Use Stripe or Razorpay for online payments.
Authentication:

Login/signup using JWT for security.
Other Features:

Responsive design.
Wishlist functionality.
User reviews and ratings for products.

